name: Abigail Hawk
biography: Abigail Hawk is an American actress best known for her recurring role as Detective Abigail Baker on the police procedural television series Blue Bloods, since 2010.

name: Sophia Bush
biography: Sophia Anna Bush (born July 8, 1982) is an American actress, director and spokesperson. She is perhaps best known for playing Detective Erin Lindsay on NBC's Chicago P.D.  Her film credits include the 2007 remake The Hitcher, John Tucker Must Die and The Narrows.

name: Victoria Rowell
biography:
From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia

Victoria "Vicki" Lynn Rowell (born May 10, 1959) is an American actress and dancer. She is best known for her portrayal of ballerina-turned-model Drucilla Winters on the CBS daytime drama The Young and the Restless, and medical examiner/pathologist Dr. Amanda Bentley on the CBS drama Diagnosis: Murder. From 1993 to 2000, she appeared on both series simultaneously.
